cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CE, cs.DS, cs.AI 

The paper deals with predicting conversions in online advertising, which involves machine learning techniques. The paper proposes a multi-task learning approach to predict different types of conversions, which is a common problem in online advertising. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves information retrieval (IR) techniques to predict conversions, which makes cs.IR (Information Retrieval) another likely sub-category. Additionally, the paper involves techniques related to computational advertising (cs.CE) and data science (cs.DS) to predict conversions. Finally, the paper involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques to solve the problem of predicting different types of conversions.
